                {
                    "name": "Disgorge Bile",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "The xilvirek retches a small pool of debilitating, acrid bile onto itself. All creatures within 30 feet take 4d6 acid damage as they inhale the bile\u2019s noxious fumes (DC 32 basic Fortitude save; on a failure, the creature is <a aonid=\"34\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">sickened  1</a>, or sickened 2 on a critical failure). The xilvirek can\u2019t Disgorge Bile again for 1d4 rounds.",
